# Frontend Styling

## CSS Framework
- **Primary**: Tailwind CSS for all styling
- **Secondary**: SCSS modules only when Tailwind insufficient
- **Global**: Minimal CSS in `app/globals.css` for theme variables

## SCSS Modules
- File naming: `ComponentName.module.scss`
- Import: `import styles from './ComponentName.module.scss'`
- Use camelCase for class names

## Theme System
- CSS custom properties in `app/globals.css`
- Light/dark mode via `html.dark` class
- Use `useTheme()` hook for theme-aware components

## Mobile-First
- Start with mobile styles, add responsive prefixes (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`)
- Minimum 44px touch targets on mobile
- Test on various screen sizes

## Aesthetics & Design Principles
- Uncluttered
- Vintage (i.e. sepia)
- Mobile-first
